Assignment 4.7
==============

Due 2009 10 12

Financial Application: Computing Future Tuition
-----------------------------------------------

Suppose that the tuition for a university is $10,000 this year and
increases 5% every year. Write a program that uses a loop to compute the
tuition in 10 years. Write another program that computes the total cost
of four years' worth of tuition starting ten years from now.

Use JOptionPane.

